headline: MetLife to Hold Conference Call for Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: NEW YORK, July 09, 2025--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that it will hold its second quarter 2025 earnings conference call and audio webcast on Thursday, August 7, 2025, from 9-10 a.m. (ET). The call will follow MetLife’s issuance of its second quarter 2025 earnings news release and Second Quarter 2025 Financial Supplement on Wednesday, August 6, 2025, after the market closes. The news release and Second Quarter 2025 Financial Supplement will also be available on the MetLife Investor
